c: 12
v: 80
t: When they despaired de changing his mind they conferred unus! Their veteris dictus vos realize ut tuus patris Perfecit taken solemn pledge ex vos DEUS? In the elapsus vos lost Joseph. Ego non sinister hoc locus my patris dedit me disponsationis alias DEUS scabinus me; He est bonus Scabinus